Steps to install terraform on Ubuntu / Ubuntu cloud server :

Install unzip

sudo apt-get install unzip
Download latest version of the terraform

wget https://releases.hashicorp.com/terraform/0.11.11/terraform_0.11.11_linux_amd64.zip  (check latest version)
Extract the downloaded file archive

unzip terraform_0.11.11_linux_amd64.zip
Move the executable into a directory searched for executables

sudo mv terraform /usr/local/bin/
or

sudo install terraform /usr/local/bin/
Run it

terraform --version 
